review: Good game, I recommend playing it. It's more realistic and overall pretty good. Although the UI isn't great, but it also isn't terrible. I got used to it pretty fast. review:
Sinceramente es una joya escondida si estas buscando un shooter para jugar con tus amigos este juego es para ti definitivamente.

Pros:

-es gratis 
-puedes jugar con tus amigos en salas privadas o publicas 
-es de pocos requisitos 
-buena personalización de armas

Contras:

-es un poco P2Win
-No se si esto sea una contra como tal pero la mayoría de los jugadores son de rusia 
-si no tienes amigos con que jugar puede que no encuentres gente (servidores vacíos) 

Puntuación final: 6/10

review:
핵쟁이가 설쳐대는데 절대 안 잡는 병신 쓰레기 게임

author: {'steamid': '76561198425222880', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 5, 'playtime_forever': 1108, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 1102, 'last_played': 1680459888}
review:
No geral é um bom jogo, mas está longe de ser perfeito.

Começando pela qualidade do jogo, podemos destacar que ele é extremamente leve, literalmente roda até em uma batata com pilha. Em segundo lugar, o jogo é bem detalhado em suas armas, a dinâmica de gameplay é divertida e os modos de jogo também.

Em termo de defeitos, o jogo está a anos sem atualização, e sinceramente acho que os devs estão mortos a esse ponto, pra piorar, o jogo tem um anti-cheat que é no mínimo duvidoso. O problema fatal é que o jogo se encontra com poucos players, mas é bem divertido com as 20 pessoas que ainda frequentam.

author: {'steamid': '76561198351442249', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 11, 'playtime_forever': 111, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 111, 'last_played': 1677220715}
review:
Line of Sight หลายคนอาจไม่ค่อยรู้จักว่าเกมนี้มีด้วยหรอ คำตอบ คือ มีครับ แต่ก่อนที่จะมาลง steam นั้นเคยอยู่ค่ายเกมออนไลน์อย่าง playpark บอกเลยว่าทำออกมาช่วงนั้นได้ดี ประสบความสำเร็จใสช่วงปี 2012
 ผ่านไป 5 ปี  Line of Sight ก็ได้ย้ายค่ายตัวไปลงในแพท steam แล้วตั้งเป็นเกม free to play ในที่สุดไม่ต้องไปโหลด playpark ให้เสียเวลาแล้ว ใครมีสตรีมก็สามารถโหลดฟรีๆได้เลย อย่างที่พอทราบกันดีนะ ว่าเกมนี้คือเกมแนวยิงปืน ที่จะแบ่ง 2 ฝั่งระหว่า แดง กับ น้ำเงินตามสไตล์ยิงปืนปกติที่จะยิงผู้เล่นคนอื่นในเกม
 สิ่งที่ต่างออกไป คือ สกิล เราสามารถติดตั้งสกิลได้หลายรูปแบบเลยไม่ว่าจะเป็น สกิลการหลบ การพุ่งชาร์ต การปล่อยจานดาวเทียม ซึ่งเป็นอะไรที่เกมอื่นไม่กล้าทำแบบนี้เลยละ ไม่มีแค่ระบบนี้ที่ดีนะ ยังมีระบบแต่งปืน ซื้อตัวละคร สามารถยื่นอายุการใช้งานอาวุธได้อีกด้วย

ข้อดีของเกมนี้
-สามารถสร้างห้องได้หลายโหมดตามที่เราอยากสร้างได้เลย กำหนดได้ว่าอยากให้ผู้เล่นนั้นทำอะไรได้บ้าง
-สามารถซื้อตัวละครได้สองรูปแบบซื้อด้วยเงินในเกม กับ เงินที่ต้องเติม
-ถ้าใครที่ชอบโหมดซอมบี้ในเกมนี้มีระบบที่เรียกว่า ฟาร์มซอมบี้ได้ ชวนเพื่อนมาฟาร์มได้อีกด้วย

ข้อเสียของเกมนี้
ตัวเกมแม้จะเปิดมานานกว่า 5 ปีแล้ว การอัพเดอร์ที่บอกเลยว่า แทบจะไม่มีอะไรเปลี่ยนไปนอกจากเสียเงิน เสียเงิน และปรับด่านใหม่เพิ่มด่านใหม่แต่มันไม่ใช่ช่วยทำให้คนที่เคยอยู่ใน playperk กลับมาเล่นได้อย่าง 100% 

ตัดหลายอย่างออกจากระบบเกม แน่นอนคนที่เคยเล่นใน ค่าย playperk นั้นจะรู้สึกเลยว่าจะมีโหมดเนื้อเรื่องเข้ามา ตอนที่ลง steam กลับถูกตัดทิ้งแบบดื้อๆเลยคนที่มาย้ายเล่นจะมองว่า ทำไมมันไม่มีเนื้อเรื่อง ยังเล่นไม่จบเลยนิ 

อีกอย่างนั้นคือ สิ่งที่สำคัญของเกมหลายๆเกมนั้นคือ เซิฟเวอร์ ในค่าย playperk เขาทำออกได้ดีนะ คนเล่นเยอะ แทบจะทุกคนเลยที่เข้ามาต่างบอกว่า เกมนี้ คือดีๆสุดเลย พอย้ายค่าย เซิฟเวอร์ทั้งหมดหายเกลี้ยงไป เหลือเพียงเซิฟเวอร์ของ รัสเซียอย่างเดียว

author: {'steamid': '76561198818432925', 'num_games_owned': 53, 'num_reviews': 93, 'playtime_forever': 3268, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 3210, 'last_played': 1682011530}
review:
Плюсы и минусы.
Итак плюсы:
+бесплатна
+легко освоить
+физика женской груди в наличии
+кастомизация оружия, можно сделать из обычного глока убервундервафлю
+разнооброзие игровых режимов
+не особо высокие требования к железу
+можно метнуть во врага фаербол или обрушить на голову метеоритный дождь
А теперь минусы:
-русификатор представляет собой непонятные надписи на языке рептилоидов с Нибиру
-на данный момент мало карт и поэтому игра быстро надоедает
-баги и вылеты
-обилие читеров
-игра не может в графон
-новичков может отпугнуть запутанный интерфейс главного меню игры, реально можно заплутать по началу
И наконец спорные моменты:
=донат особой роли не играет, но все-равно очень бросается в глаза
=на данный момент людей играющих в эту игру маловато
=игра быстро осваивается и столь же быстро надоедает
Игре еще предстоит развиваться и на данный момент все не так уж и плохо. Но если через пол-года или год ничего не изменится то Line of Sight обречена на провал. А пока я рекомендую эту игру тем, у кого нет денег на более достойные проекты.
Ну что господа, игра умирает и это прискорбно. За полгода добавили одну снайперскую винтовку, убрали корявый русификатор и фиксанули пару багов. Все. Если вы хотите и дальше сношать труп этой игрули, то милости прошу. Он еще теплый и пока не начал попахивать, но скоро будет невыносимо вонять и покроется трупными пятнами.
Баланс в игре есть, лучшие оружие которое я кастомизировал это калаш нацепив 16х оптику и все обвесы, и дигл и поставил на него 16х прицел это моя мини винтовка очень добротная, аим в игре топ по круче, чем варфейсе, я даже с ак-74 просто анигилировал все сервера бегая с этой пукалкой.
Играть в неё можно на 2022 сервера работают и онлайн есть, но маленький. ПВП с другом создав сови сервера самое то, игра пойдёт на пару вечерков не более.
Жалко что в игре низкий онлайн, и игру так плохо оценивают. Игра играбелная.

10 ЛУЧШИЙ БЕСПЛАТНЫЙ ШУТЕР ИЗ 10

author: {'steamid': '76561199109813370', 'num_games_owned': 123, 'num_reviews': 66, 'playtime_forever': 2599, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 2599, 'last_played': 1640208036}
review:
привет все равно эти обзоры здесь не кто не читает так что напишу рецепт блинчиков))))
Продукты
Молоко (любое, которое вам по душе) - 700 мл
Яйца куриные - 3 шт.
Мука - грамм 200-250 (я на глаз сыплю, по густоте определяем, хватит или нет)
Масло сливочное - 1 ст. ложка (растопить)
(или используем 1,5-2 ст. ложки растительного, благодаря маслу блинчики не будут прилипать к сковороде)
Соль - по вкусу
Сахар - по вкусу
(соли и сахара немного, но в равных количествах - блины должны быть ни солеными, ни сладкими, нейтральными, чтобы подходили и к варенью, и к сметанке)
1. Яйца выбиваем в глубокую мисочку, превращаем в однородную массу (у меня венчик для таких дел). В любом случае, это лучше делать ВРУЧНУЮ, а не блендерами и т.п., размешивая все до мелочей.

2. Туда же вливаем половину(!) молока (оставшуюся половину потом добавим). Мешаем.

3. Сыплем муку. Чтобы было густовато, с расчетом на то, что еще будет молоко и масло. Мешаем-мешаем-мешаем! Да хорошенько!=)

4. Топим сливочное масло, добавляем в тесто (или добавляем растительное масло). Вливаем остальное молоко и опять, несложно догадаться, перемешиваем. О-о-очень хорошо. Я минут 5 мешала.

5. Итак, тесто готово, оно должно быть жидким, примерно как 1-процентный кефир. Сковородку раскаляем, смазываем (не наливаем, а именно смазываем) растительным маслом, чтобы в сковороде не было лужи масла, ибо наш блин будет убогим=( У меня антипригарная сковорода, поэтому я смазывала всего раза 2-3 в течение всего процесса.

6. Ну что ж, теперь самое интересное. Зачерпываем половинку поварешки теста - на сковородку. И-и-и... оп-па!!! крутим её, распределяя тесто по всему дну сковородки. Всегда себя ощущаю крутым поваром, когда так мастерски управляюсь с блином!=)

Если первый блин вышел комом, не огорчаемся - он или сильно толстый, или очень тонкий, или масла много... Зато после этого первого блина мы увидели свою ошибку и дальше грешить не будем, дальше все будет удачно!

author: {'steamid': '76561197984705404', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 7, 'playtime_forever': 8812, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 7935, 'last_played': 1659485135}
review: Great game! Without taking in any other factors this is a fun way to pass the time! Line of Sight has interesting additional game mechanics that makes it different than your normal arena FPS(psyc-powers).  The community is far, half the time someone is cheating and the other half think you are cheating.  I would suggest, take some time to get the ability usage in rotation and see if it fits your play-style, before getting to worked up about people just dominating.  Has a good size gun library and each one has a selection of customizations for the gun people out there.  If you want to expand your selection of guns you will have to grab your credit card though. All in all, good game, wild matches and guns to have fun; don't take the trolls to serious they can't help themselves.  Have fun and i'll catch you in my sights!

review:
После этой xyйни смотришь на другие шутеры и понимаешь - насколько же там хорошо проработан неткод,даже в убогих пapaшax по типу PUBG и Arma где на 100 человек выделяется кластер 1 ядро 800мхз и 256мб оперативки нет таких проблем.

Сломанные хитбоксы,вы6лядcкий неткод и 8 тикрейта,это то,что осталось от когда то перспективной игры с уникальными механиками.

Если вам по кайфу сосать члeны у индусов с 224 пинга умирая за стенами или от того что стрелять по ним надо на перед при том что в игре нет балистики - то добро пожаловать.

Серьезно... Я никогда не думал что такое скажу - но лучше установи валорант чел.

review: Когда мне было 15 лет, и я ходил срать бятя всё время как-бы невзначай крутился возле толчка, и всё спрашивал, что ты там затих, почему тебя не слышно? первый раз я не ответил, так он начал ломиться в дверь, и орать, что ты там молчишь, что с тобой? начал материться, и говорить, что вообще дверь с петель снимет, алсо, батя ругался, если я сру и не смываю, причём не просто вконце срания, а непосредственно после вылезания какашки, мотивировал это тем, что воняет, и сам потом мне говорил: вот я какну и смываю, и ты так делай! однажды я срать сел, и слышу, батя где-то у двери встал в отдалении, ну я жопу вытер, и на пол накарачики присел, а там щель очень широкая снизу у двери, ну я в щель и смотрю, а там батя на карачиках сидит и в щель смотрит, и мне говорит: ты чё? ебанутый? чё ты там делаешь? батя кстати всё время какие-то травы пьёт, чтобы срать часто, срёт по 5 раз в день, а потом говорит, что жопу жжёт, и ещё пердит он. пиздец короче! реальная история. я не тролль

review: Oyun çok güzel fakat birazcık ilgiye ve reklama ihtiyacı var. Oyuncu sayısı çok az. Ana ekran dizaynı biraz daha basit yapılmalı ve rekabetçi gibi oyun modları eklenmeli ve rekabetçi lobisi eklenmesi gerek. Onun dışında oyuncu tüm silahlara erişebilmeli. Bu silahlardaki seviyeli sistem kötü nedeni ise oyuncu sayısı az olduğu için yüksek levelli bir oyuncuya karşı şansımız kalmıyor gibi. :/  Tabi bunlar düzeltilebilecek şeyler ilk olarak oyuncu sayısını çoğaltması gerek yani biraz reklam lazım.

author: {'steamid': '76561199206811909', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 13, 'playtime_forever': 12, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 12, 'last_played': 1652927544}
review: Es un muy buen juego hasta ahora lo que he jugado me ha encantado, me gusta todo desde las armas y las habilidades que le podemos poner a nuestros personajes, y un nivel muy bueno de personalizacion del arma, creo que deberian de mejorar un poco el lanzagranadas su radio de daño es bastante pequeño entiendo que puede ser muy op si matara a muchos de un solo tiro pero por lo menos dejarlos heridos no estaria mal y solo matar a alguien directamente si le pega la explosion directo asi que por ese lado ponerle un lanzagranadas a un arma se siente bastante inutil tal vez tambien podrian agregarle una escopeta montable a los rifles de asalto eso estaria bien, el gamplay como los mapas y modos de juegos tambien son muy variados, sin duda recomiendo este juego un muy buen shooter ojala y mas gente lo jugara eso es lo que le hace falta al juego mas promocion aca en latinoamerica y norteamerica.

Телефонный звонок, трубку берет ребенок. Шепотом:
- Алло?

Ребенок (тихо-тихо):
- Да, но он занят...
- А мама дома?
- Она тоже очень-очень занята...
- А еще дома кто-нибудь есть?
- Дяденьки милиционеры и пожарные...
- Ну, позови тогда хотя бы их!
- Не могу, они тоже очень заняты...

- Они меня повсюду ищут и найти не могут...

review:
Играл год назад или даже больше. Есть свои плюсы и минусы (пишу то что было год назад и более)
> Минусы - Как-то странно локализован русский язык, он есть не везде и иногда коряво, частично слова остаются на английском.
> Плюсы - 100% стоит попробовать установить и познакомится, хороший движок привыкаешь быстро, уникальный gameplay, свои фишки которых мало где найдешь у других игр известных мне или в стим. Современное реальное оружие с хорошим набором оснащения и кастомизации + сверхспособности.

author: {'steamid': '76561198059281936', 'num_games_owned': 420, 'num_reviews': 29, 'playtime_forever': 568, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 106, 'last_played': 1672647044}
review:
Update: 1/2/2023

On a whim I decided to look at old games I haven't really played from my steam library and reinstalled this game. That was a mistake because this game is hilariously bad. There is one server, and if you get terrible ping in western Europe servers, well you can get bent because you have no other option. 

This game has no idea what it is doing, it has some of the worst hit registration/ hit boxes I have ever seen on a steam game and I've played a lot of garbage games. Sometimes entire magazines wont register, other times a shot in the foot will instantly kill with a headshot, its a complete coin flip if you win gun fights or you could just head glitch and not have a head hitbox entirely, you could be that guy in the lobby. To put into perspective on how bad this game is, its most popular 2 maps do not even have textures. Do not give any money to this trash fire and move along.

review: Finde das etwas schade, dass das Spiel sehr wenige spielen. Ab- und an sind mal 3-4 Server online, aber grundsätzlich ist man mit maximal 10 Leuten der einzige der heute und genau jetzt spielt. Würde um einiges mehr Spaß machen, wenn das mehr spielen würden. Dafür, dass es F2P ist und recht simple aufgebaut hat das eine echte Weiterempfehlung verdient. Der Shooting-Faktor ist auch recht realistisch, nur die Grafik lässt zu wünschen übrig. Aber ich bin auch so ein Typ der nach wie vor noch Stonehenge oder AOE 2, Anno, C&C  und andere Retrospiele feiert. Jedenfalls immer geil für ein Sniper 1-1 mit einem Kollegen.

author: {'steamid': '76561197993070333', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 73, 'playtime_forever': 68, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 34, 'last_played': 1637574910}
review:
I really want to recommend this game but I just can’t at the moment. I enjoy playing it and it brings back so many good memories of MW2 but there are just too many problems with it currently. If the devs fix/change anything I'll update my review.
Pros
Weapon/Character Customization
Not Pay to Win (Yes I'm serious)
Runs good
High TTK
Classic Vibe
Weapon Balance (Pretty good, there are a few weps that need a nerf atm though.)

Cons
Hitreg - Terrible atm, constantly die around corners
Hit boxes - Same with hitreg
Head glitching - Major problem that needs fixing
GP earn rate - Needs to be increased or weapon prices lowered
Mantle/Flash Animation - Are terrible and get you killed so much and need to be removed.
Player falling physics - don't try to slide down a hill
Flashlight - I get its a tactical light but it shouldn't be like looking at the sun
Maps - Pretty meh, a lot of them could use adjusting.
"Super Powers/Abilities" - I hate them, but I play classic anyways
UI - Could be simpler

If you want to read it properly formatted: http://steamcommunity.com/id/Juggernaut_Drive/recommended/436520/

I'll try to expand on my points in case anyone is interested in more of what I mean. Before that however I do want to mention that I do enjoy the game. I enjoy it so much and it reminds me of when I used to play COD all day on xbox when I was a kid. Now to get to the points.

The Pros:
Weapon/Character Customization - Nothing much to say just it's pretty in depth and you can make so many different variants. The only real thing their lacking here are the skins. I assume they will add more skins in time though.
Not Pay to Win - It's not pay to win which is great! People who say it's pay to win don't put any time into the game and look don't at the weapon stats. If you did than you would find out that most of the weapons you buy don't have any better stats that the ones you start with. Now of course there are some weapons that are better than others atm but you get that with every AAA game that has a price tag of ~$60 so I'm sure the developers will address those in the future.
Runs good - Nothing more to say really. It runs good and I have had no problems with it.
High TTK - Very high time to kill which is great. But if you pair that with bad hitreg then you get a load of problems (hitreg is talked about more below).
Classic Vibe - Reminds me of the COD4/MW2 days.
Weapon Balance - As talked about in the not p2w section, weapon balance is pretty good at the time of this review.

The Cons:
Hitreg - It's really bad atm and I mean REALLY bad. Your shots don't hit and you die around corners constantly. I don't know if I just didn't notice it when I first started playing, but I noticed it after one of their updates. So I'm not sure if it was always bad or if that update broke it.
Hit boxes - The female hitbox is smaller than the males (not the bad point) but when you have bad hitreg/head glitching it makes you thing that the hit boxes are also broken. I don't know if it’s that or the hitreg, but something is definitely off.
Head glitching - Major problem that needs fixing. You see the tippy top of their head and they see your whole body. Plus, pair that with the hitboxes and you can't hit their head.
GP earn rate - Needs to be increased or weapon prices lowered. I have around 28 hours into the game (not all playtime) and I currently have around ~170,000 GP. Which seems like a lot of GP but when you add that I played very heavily during the valentine event and the new achievements I got (since it was a new account) it's really not that much. If it wasn't a valentine event and I wasn't a new player I would have significantly less GP for that time played. Yes yes I know you get GP from missions, achievements, leaderboard rankings and at the end of every match.
Missions - Math is based off a 30 day month. So if you do EVERY single mission a month you get around 114,000GP. Daily Missions = 90,000GP, Weekly Missions = 12,000GP, Monthly Missions = 12,000GP. So 1 month of my time isn't worth enough for ONE primary weapon (about 214,000GP)?
Achievements - Yes you get GP for achievements and you get the reward ONCE. This seems good and fair since there are 408 achievements but it's not. More than like half of the achievements are weapon related which means you CAN'T get the reward until you unlock the weapon. The weapons go as follows; K2 I = 30 kills, K2 II = 300 kills, K2 III = 3000 kills. I shouldn't have to say much more about why relying on achievements for GP is so stupid.
Leaderboard - You get 20,000GP if you place in the top 4% in every section every month.
End of match reward - You get like 100GP which is pointless. 1000 games of 100GP = 100,000GP.
Mantle/Flash Animation - Are terrible and get you killed so much and need to be removed. There stupid animations that are not needed. The flash puts a hand up in front of your view and you can’t shoot until the hand goes down. It also lasts LONGER than the actual flash like wtf. The mantle locks you into a mantle animation when you try and jump over something.
Player falling physics - You get stuck and jitter down the hill or object that’s slanted.
Flash light - I get its a tactical light but it shouldn't be like looking at the sun. It's gameplay breaking, way to bright atm.
Maps - Pretty meh, a lot of them could use adjusting. The S&D maps are by far the best but come with problems as well. A lot of the sites only have 2 entrances and then its closed off.
"Super Powers/Abilities" - Hate them since you need to have the medic one equipped or you’re at a huge disadvantage.
UI - Very confusing when you first load it up and could be simpler.

Gra graficznie troszkę się postarzała ale nie drastycznie, fajnie było by zobaczyć w niej  ponownie pełne serwery aczkolwiek kiedyś miałem wrażenie że gra ma model pay 2 win.

review:
This game will force u to do the fastest alt + f4's ever.
This game is almost dead so the only way to play it is with friends or with bots , and even when you will find someone to play with , its a guy against u , with lvl 130+ , who is shooting you through every wall and with pre fire , even tho you are crouching which makes you silent.
You CANT do any good score because of that , and servers with auto balance are not balanced at all , many time you will see matches with one team lvls 1-5 and the other 40-100 , good balance ngl.
Buying characters with real currency , as long with weapons and skins.
Dont play this game , its just a waste of time.

author: {'steamid': '76561198352607192', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 12, 'playtime_forever': 234, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 234, 'last_played': 1633590921}
review:
이 게임에는 여러 문제점이 있다.
1. 맵에 자잘한 버그가 많음. 만들다 만 느낌임.
2. 사람이 없음. 유럽 서버에서 해서 핑차이가 많이 남.
3. 근접무기 판정이 병신임. 존나 쑤셔댔는데 하나 죽이기 어려움.
4. 동시에 키를 눌렀을 때 씹히는 경우가 많음. 장비 문제가 아니라 그냥 게임자체가 병신임.
5. 무기 시스템도 한번 사면 되는 것이 아니라 기간제임.
6. 한명 죽이기 생각보다 어려움. 대부분 권총은 한탄창 쏟아부어야하고 SMG는 진짜 근접에서 LMG는 시발
앉으면 조준 안 해도 존나 잘맞음.

서든 대용으로 해볼려 했는데 기분만 잡침

review:
I really love this game and have no known issues by far. Its free, I cant find pay to win and spam and annoying advertising. It should be the rule but we all know these days is not. I really enjoy that, the mecanics are well implemented, it has a great optimization, the only kind of negative issue is there are few servers. But never encountered any lag, any toxic comunity, hackers, etc.

I try to play this game almost every day and Im am really enjoying it.
I want to give this good feedback specially to the developers, they really deserve it.

Totally recomended.

author: {'steamid': '76561198980478902', 'num_games_owned': 48, 'num_reviews': 7, 'playtime_forever': 47, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 46, 'last_played': 1626420426}
review:
Не знаю, что написать, поэтому напишу рецепт оладушек.

ИНГРЕДИЕНТЫ на 4 порции:
Сахар - 3 столовые ложки
Молоко - 200 мл
Соль - по вкусу
Пшеничная мука - 200 г
Яйцо куриное - 1 штука
Растительное масло - 50 мл
Уксус 9%-ный - ½ чайной ложки
Сода - ½ чайной ложки
ИНСТРУКЦИЯ ПРИГОТОВЛЕНИЯ:
1. Муку, сахар и щепотку соли смешайте.
2. Яйцо взбейте с молоком, добавьте гашеную уксусом соду. Добавьте муку. Замесите до однородной массы. Тесто должно получиться густым. По необходимости добавьте еще муки.
3. Порциями примерно со столовую ложку вылейте тесто на раскаленную сковороду. Обжарьте оладушки с обеих сторон на среднем огне.

review: I seriously liked this game. One of my favorites. It had a neat concept (psionics + FPS), pretty great graphics (especially considering the bulk of development happened in 2017), and an awesome community. I wish they could find funding to really evolve the game further. Sadly, not much has changed in recent years. I do recommend the game for anyone looking for an easy to learn, but hard to master FPS game that doesn't feel super mainstream.

author: {'steamid': '76561198047650299', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 11, 'playtime_forever': 577, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 577, 'last_played': 1619649378}
review:
Лютое ведро помоев. Видите системные требования? А вот хрен там плавал, вам ссут в уши ещё до этапа скачивания игры, что говорить о внутриигровом наполнении. Она у меня на компе с 4 гиговой видюхой на минималках лагает сильнее современных проектов. И комп далеко за пределами рекомендуемого, в лучшую сторону разумеется.
Забудьте нахрен о контенте в этой игре - за ним стоит две вещи: пэйволл что китайская стена и гринд, на уровне пожизненной ссылки в урановые шахты.
И вместе со всем этим встречаем восхитительный матчмейкинг, где в одном лобби сталкиваются лбами люди от 1 уровня до 200, бездарный маппинг, преимущество донатных пушек/снаряги над стандартом и получаем позорное количество активного комьюнити (чаще из тех, кто имел глупость заносить сюда деньги и тратить время). Игра заслуженно обитает на днище стима, хотя лучше бы её уже отсюда выпнули на обочину игровой движухи. Видеть такой кал мамонта, который лишь подтверждает мнение об ущербности бесплатных проектов как существующих, так и самой идеи в целом - обидно, ибо правда глазки нашинковывает.
Единственное что мне понравилось в этой поделке и где я провёл большую часть времени - кастомизатор оружия с дальнейшим тестом на полигоне. По-сути, 80% времени проведённого в этой игре я провёл именно в магазине, меню свистоперделок и полигоне.
(Фанаты Трахова, можете не говорить что в вашей игре всё равно лучше. Мы знаем.)

review: целом игра довольно не плохая. Представляет из себя шутер от первого лица. В игре присутствует мультиплеер. В игре хорошая графика, не плохой геймплей, хорошая физика, реалистичные звуки и многое другое. В игре большие и хорошо проработанные карты. Так же в игре присутствует возможность модифицировать своё оружие. Несмотря на то что у игры достаточно положительных качеств, по сути игра является очередным клоном игры Warface.

author: {'steamid': '76561198196600910', 'num_games_owned': 418, 'num_reviews': 54, 'playtime_forever': 293, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 266, 'last_played': 1620576001}
review:
'Okay' best sums up the game.
It's not good by any means, but enough to last a while.

Game's basically dead, a lot of that going to VERY BAD anti-cheat system.
Apart from that, the game doesn't have much holding it up, and other Asian shooters offer way more than this one does.
The game occasionally has an event or two that'll bring people to the game for a weekend to about Monday or Tuesday depending on the event, but otherwise it's nothing that's going to stay.

I recommend it if you want the most basic, fast sniping, and accuracy based head picking I've ran into in an Asian FPS. Though otherwise, you're gonna be better off looking elsewhere to see if there's something else that offers you a better experience.
Apart from that, the gameplay is actually the only thing making me rate this a yes from me. It's so energetic, fun, and fast paced, something you don't often find in even GOOD Asian FPS titles.
This game excels here.

author: {'steamid': '76561198282504121', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 4, 'playtime_forever': 156, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 122, 'last_played': 1612875483}
review:
The concept of self-fund publishing was extreme, but sadly poor executed.

Pros:
-Somewhat extreme gun customisation
-ESP skill thingie

Cons:
-Inefficient Anti-Hacking Program
-P2W Weapons
-No support since 2019, which became crucial

Avoid this game, until they gave an update. Surprising though, the server still active.  Hacker somewhat infested in this game, making it less playable than it should be. Anyhow, soon or later they might ask another publisher to take care of this game, unless they let this game dead or pick Nexon for their publisher... Until now, just check another F2P FPS like Ironsight.

Update: Someone uploaded the screenshot about the conversation with Chris Kim, as he stated he will not continue to contribute LoS about a 7 months ago. The conclusion? LoS is dead, but he'll planned to make another game and Line of Sight 2, which I really doubt about it.

review: This game is a piece of SHIT and whoever developed this trash should be ashamed. Sniper shots don't count, I hit multiple headshots but died instead because THE FUCKING HEADSHOTS DON'T COUNT. Not only that but this trash piece of garbage has a fixed spawn system so hackers can spawn kill you as much as they want. I played this game for only 5 minutes and I already HATE it!!! IT also looks like a pay to win game just like Crossfire, Combat Arms and other trash games out there. Not worthy of my time, or anybody else's. Why is this even out here for download, how come this game still has functioning servers? If you want to play a decent FPS, go play Ironsight. It's full of tryhards but at least you'll have an actual chance of having fun.

author: {'steamid': '76561198288058950', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 2721, 'playtime_forever': 407, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 8, 'last_played': 1709798701}
review:
Это хорошая обложка и фотографии. Но когда вы входите, это что-то другое ...

Когда вы входите в игру, первое, что я замечаю, это то, что она была на английском языке, с английским нет проблем. Потому что сколько вы собираетесь читать в MM Shooter?

Что, если у игры есть сервер в Азии И в Европе, Европа будет лучшим, если вы находитесь в Америке, по понятным причинам.

Войдите в игру, и первое, что вы заметите, - это зула. Но это что, если бы Зула были более «оригинальными»?
В кавычках, так как он больше копирует Cod.

Хорошо то, что игра не так уж плоха, она занимательна, если вам нравится что-то более «бешеное». Что Zula XD

Плохо то, что у него есть только Сервер, В АЗИИ И ЕВРОПЕ, а не в США (по крайней мере). Если вы собираетесь играть в нее, я рекомендую сеть с объемом памяти более 5 мегабайт.
И вторая плохая вещь - это Free Fire или Rush Fire. Так как попасть в Headshot можно без прицеливания, а стрелять только по таким
brazuca в кэжуал из CS: GO.

это оно

7,90 / 10

author: {'steamid': '76561198862411731', 'num_games_owned': 242, 'num_reviews': 168, 'playtime_forever': 19, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 19, 'last_played': 1605070589}
review:
Esta bueno La portada y las fotos. Pero cuando entras es otra cosa...

Cuando entre al juego, lo primero que note es que estaba en ingles, ningun problema con el ingles. ¿Porque que tanto te vas a poner a leer en un Shooter MM?.

Lo que si es que el el juego tiene server en Asia Y en Europa, Quedando como mejor Europa si estas en America, por obvias razones. 

Entre a una partida, y lo primero que note es que es un Zula. Pero es un ¿Que pasaria si Zula Fuera mas "Original"?,
Entre comillas, ya que es mas copia a Cod.

Lo bueno es que no esta tan mal el juego, Es entretenido, si te gusta algo mas "frenetico". Que Zula XD

Lo malo es que solo tenga Server, EN ASIA Y EUROPA, y no es EE.UU (Por lo menos). Si vas a jugarlo, te recomiendo una red que tenga mas de 5 megas. 
Y lo segundo malo es que es un Free Fire o un Rush Fire. Ya que podes meter Headshot sin apuntar, y solo disparando a tal
brazuca en casual de CS:GO. 

Eso es todo

7,90/10

author: {'steamid': '76561198380165245', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 12, 'playtime_forever': 99952, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 410, 'playtime_at_review': 197, 'last_played': 1712415324}
review:
チーター大暴走、チートパーティ、チーター育成ゲーム
世界中の精鋭チーターが集い、チートを競い合いチーター同士が罵り合う面白いゲーム
過去に一度もチートツール使用者をＢＡＮした事実がないらしく、
上位ランカーのほとんどがハッキングツール使用者。
むしろなんで使わずにプレイしているのかと聞かれるくらいです。
なので堂々とチートプレイしてもこの運営は大丈夫みたいです。
しかしながら、チーターを煽ったり、チャットでチートを指摘するとこちらがＢANされます。
しかも迅速にＢＡＮされます(二度ほど経験済み)
運営は基本的に日本人プレイヤーを嫌っているので目をつけられたらまともなプレイはまず不可能です。
上記に基づきチーターはどんなに煽ってもＢＡＮされません。こちらが何度通報しても無対応です。
さらに驚くのは半数以上のチーターがスチームのバッジをつけている事
チーターに煽られても狩られても気にせずプレイできる人、M指向の方はどうぞ

review:
Au 11/09/2020, les cheaters sont nombreux et ne se cachent pas. Vous les croiserez une TdM sur 2 au minimum.
"TgStChen", "Nosferatu", "Lessss", "Niezla" et plein plein d'autres.... ces noms vous vous souviendrez.
Vous trouverez en une seule recherche, sur google, Youtube les tutoriels pour les telecharger.
Ils existent depuis 2017 mais certains sont maintenant obsolète, à l'époque le jeux était maintenu.
Aujourd'hui, vous ne risquez plus rien, les personnes citées ci-dessus ne se sont jamais fait ban.

Une astuce hyper fun, d'experience, les hacks avec autofocus ne semblent pas tous fonctionner  si vous jouez avec un Light sur votre arme :)

author: {'steamid': '76561198452336073', 'num_games_owned': 49, 'num_reviews': 23, 'playtime_forever': 1475, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 660, 'last_played': 1645960760}
review: Line of Sight ist ein kostenloses Ballerspiel, wo man mal schön ne Runde gegeneinander Ballern kann. Es geht halt gerne mal schnell zur Sache, aber so ist das halt bei Ballerspielen. Das Spiel läuft auch auf normalen Laptops, was heutzutage bei Ballerspielen ja nicht mehr so üblich ist -.- (Mein Laptop: CPU: 2,4 GHz, Grafikchip: Intel HD Graphics 4000, Arbeitsspeicher: 8 GB). Am Anfang musste ich mich etwas eingewöhnen, aber man kommt eigentlich gut rein. Man kann seine Waffen so anpassen, wie man es gerne haben möchte. Außerdem gibt es viele Errungenschaften, die man bekommen kann. Übrigens kann man in dem Spiel für eine Sekunde sehr schnell rennen, oder eine Riesenexplosion machen. Aber man kann natürlich auch ohne die Extras spielen, wenn man realistisch spielen möchte. Ist aber eine interessante Funktion. Da das Spiel kostenlos ist und nicht sehr groß ist, wie die heutigen Ballerspiele leider fast alle sind, kann man es sich ja schnell mal runterladen und es ausprobieren. Leider ist aber alles auf Englisch. Auf der Kaufseite steht zwar, dass Deutsch unterstützt wird, aber ich sehe halt nur Englisch zum auswählen. Man bekommt beim ersten Spielstart übrigens eine Einführung in das Spiel und erhält danach eine Errungenschaft. Leider kommt die Einführung direkt und man hat keine Möglichkeit die erst später zu machen. Einstellungen können also erst nach der Einführung vorgenommen werden. Trotzdem kann ich dieses Spiel empfehlen. Mir gefällt es gut.

review:
O jogo é bom, mas poderia ser melhor com esses fatores:
-Server Sul-Americano, por usar o servidor da europa causa muito lag pra qualquer brasileiro.
-Comunidade maior, o jogo poderia se empenhar em deixa-lo agradável para as pessoas, por exemplo, o loading é uma foto apenas.
-Suporte, os desenvolvedores poderiam ouvir mais as análises e os players do game, pois o jogo está o mesmo desde 2015 (joguei em outra conta).
no dia de hoje, o jogo não pode ser recomendado, mas em 2017 talvez poderia ser um jogo bem divertido e competitivo.

author: {'steamid': '76561197998280696', 'num_games_owned': 3109, 'num_reviews': 606, 'playtime_forever': 2613, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 2613, 'last_played': 1592776000}
review:
Um jogo de armas que pode ir muito além do tiroteio convencional. Temos as opções de simplesmente jogar o clássico ou com as habilidades especiais e as chamadas psiônicas. São habilidades até realistas considerando como uso tecnológico.
Vários modos também como captura de bandeira, duelo, procurar e destruir, mata-mata de equipe ou livre.

As armas são compradas fora da partida. É difícil tornar competitivo esse tipo de sistema. Você pode jogar sempre com a arma que gosta, mas precisa do dinheiro dentro do jogo para ficar renovando. Achei fácil conseguir pelas missões diárias.

author: {'steamid': '76561198030230602', 'num_games_owned': 786, 'num_reviews': 87, 'playtime_forever': 33, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 33, 'last_played': 1590780989}
review:
No, though yes, if you want to just have a load of laughs with a few lads in some scuffed ass game that looks like it was a copy of a copy of some fps.

This is one of those games that are so bad in pretty much every way but the core gameplay takes little skill and fairly fun to  mess around in, that is, until you meet the p2w shit which this game is full of, sure you can kill your enemy and yoink their gun (which will quite likely outperform the sort of bottom of the barrel crap you start with) but if you never do then you'll just get wiped. 

The last and perhaps more disappointing and understandable thing is that this game is semi-dead, sure you'll get some stragglers here and there but you're gonna need to probably catch the game on "peaks" or just have a large circle of friends to play with.
Overall, not a game that needs to be taken serious and a solid 4/10
(shows 0.6 hrs on record but apparently it deleted the playtime i had previously)

author: {'steamid': '76561197981522694', 'num_games_owned': 810, 'num_reviews': 11, 'playtime_forever': 38, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 38, 'last_played': 1590680569}
review:
Why did I Buy this... wait, *DID* I buy this?
No, free to play... and it shows, you're either stuck with a flattop M4 or you're handing over your credit card.

Honestly I'm not sure why this is in my library, I think maybe I was expecting either a VR experience or a replacement for Ghost Recon phantom and I got neither... just some cheap knock-off, low-quality Call of Duty wannabee that does not really live up to it's advertisement.

If you're jumping in expecting full range customizable weapons; nope... none of that.
Maps are tiny and usually wholly symmetrical; which means every map gets chocked within seconds and it becomes really boring.

SMART players will use the 30-day "Trial" for 'premium' weapons to come up with three distinct load outs, suitable for whatever situation you might find yourself in.... and assuming that unlike me you'll LAST those thirty days, rather than less than 30 minutes, you (MIGHT) be tempted to invest in ONE loadout.

I tried to get rid of that horrible first-half-that-is-a-before/after face my character had by adding a helmet; but apparently armored cranial protection and mutual mug mitigation is a PREMIUM feature.

I wouldn't recommend this game to anyone, but then again, I prefer coop- and single-player exploits over this type of junk.

author: {'steamid': '76561198073300219', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 15, 'playtime_forever': 5517, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 774, 'last_played': 1667629162}
review:
The game is pretty fun if you're into mindless PVP, the only challenge is finding a time where people are playing. There's only 2 regions and for the most part the Asia region is empty and the other is full of people with 200+ ping so it can get frustrating.
The AI matches are utterly useless in combat, so they're only good for earning some quick cash to buy guns or attachments.
Despite the low population the gameplay itself it actually pretty fun so I would recommend this game if you have a group of friends to join you.

Edit: You can pay real money to get a helmet that helps prevent headshots so that's pretty unfortunate.

author: {'steamid': '76561197976260411', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 19, 'playtime_forever': 46177, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 1049, 'last_played': 1668093946}
review: This game is a fun, team based, areana shooter with some good combat, interesting add on powers, good character and weapon models, and a small number of interesting maps.  Its biggest flaw is probably that there doesn't seem to be any anti-cheat system - so in some matches the fact that some players are running "see you through walls" or "aiming" cheats becomes all too obvious.  Another problem is that the client UI doesn't support any option for a "color blind mode" - so the 5% of the population (10% among males) that is color blind will probably be at a big disadvantage by not being able to see red that is used to identify the bad guys very well (which is the most common type of color blindness).  In this day and age, all games should support alternate colors for identifying enemies other than than red!

review: Сначала шутер мне показался говном, и я удалил его)) после промежутка времени я скачал снова ету игру, сыграл 20 часов и я готов вынести своё мнение - игра недооценена, по сравнению с донатной помойкой Warface ета игра даёт больше возможностей в кастомизации, здесь приятная стрельба с одинаковым спрей-паттерном и всё оружие можно купить за игровую валюту(что бы купить Снайперку Скаут мне понадобилась неделя игры)Также про кастомизацию - базовое оружие можно изменить до неузнаваемости и визуально, и по характеристикам.Карты здесь разнообразные, особенно хочу отметить Ферму и Зимнюю, а также почти все карты из режима Каждый сам за себя.  Вердикт - игра незаслуженно никем почти не играется, а если играют, то очень высокие лвлы...

review:
El juego es interesante, en cuanto a controles, mecánicas y gráficos es bastante bueno, también me gusta bastante el sistema de personalización aunque le agregaría más objetos (para variar un poco más las cosas).
El único problema que le veo es que solo hay 2 servers: europeo y asiático, lo cual es un gran problema para muchos, yo diría que hagan más servers (incluyendo uno latinoamericano).
Para concluir solo queda decir que es un juego con potencial.
7/10 (le podría poner 8 de no ser por la escasez de servers)
Saludos!!!!

author: {'steamid': '76561197990231010', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 1, 'playtime_forever': 8053, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 1380, 'last_played': 1704967300}
review:
Первый обзор в стиме. Не пишу обзоров не мое это, но эту игру, кажется, незаслуженно поливают какахами.
Попробую внести свой в клад в восстановлении справедливости.
 
Очень понравилась игра.
Динамичный шутан, с хорошей кастомизацией оружия. 
Понравилась динамика передвижений. неплохая механика стрельбы.
Графика простовата, но приятная. Звуки слабоваты, но отвращения не вызывают


Плюсы:
+ Отличная оптимизация даже с учетом скромных системных требований.
+ Динамика отличная. скорость спринта и псионик способности позволяют быстро найти замес и при необходимости быстро выйти.
+ Дизайн карт хорошо продуман (по крайней мере тех на которых я успел поиграть) позволяет реализовать любой стиль игры почти на любой карте (опять же говори за те, в которые успел поиграть их, наверное, около 10).
+ Довольно много игровых режимов.
+ Доступность годных стволов за игровые деньги и на очень ранних этапах игры (SCAR-H доступен с 4лвл. Сейчас у меня 16 и чуть больше 20 часов наиграно, и я не чувствую потребности менять пушку).
+ Оружие настраивается под свой стиль игры.
+ Есть какие-то перки для персонажа (combat mastery). Видимо они неплохо сбалансированы и не дают каких-то гигантских преимуществ, ибо я о них узнал только вчера, но не сказал бы что без них меня как-то щемили.
+ Бесплатная. Донат за косметику. остальное можно насобирать игровым путем. Вполне можно играть, не потратив ни копейки.
Пушки можно попробовать бесплатно - комплекты бесплатной снаряги меняются каждую неделю. 

Минусы:
- Мало игроков.
- Из первого минуса следует и хромой матчмэейкинг.  можно попасть как к задротам, так и к ракообразным в катку. автобаланс работает слабенько, видимо из-за малого онлайна.

Выводы:

 Графодрочеры- лучше проходите мимо, тут не на что смотреть, остальным любителям соревновательных шутеров, ИМХО стоит попробовать, тем более что для этого не нужно платить ни копейки и стартовых денег с головой хватает на то чтоб купить снарягу и полностью оценить, что да как.

author: {'steamid': '76561198047276038', 'num_games_owned': 305, 'num_reviews': 119, 'playtime_forever': 576, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 227, 'last_played': 1613478612}
review:
This game is a VERY good creation which is focusing on many gamemodes, it's like CS:GO but without those Cyka-Blyats and cheating kiddos everywhere around which I massively appreciate in my 3 (As of writing this review) hours of gameplay.

The weapon mechanics are just more than great, it provides you with selection of weaponry that you can choose from, within just that, you can also customize your weaponry, have more damage and therefore your accuracy suffers under it, the moment you change something to good, you also get a minus within, which is also quite balancing.

Weapongameplay is quite good, you can choose from the gamemodes you wanna play, whether it be with or without heavy weaponry, if you for example appreciate handguns more than heavy weaponry, just select it and you find yourself with a pistol over the entire game that you're playing.

What the game also provides is one of my most favorite, respawn times, unlike TF2 or other online-shooter games, if you die, you may get that typical showscreen who killed you, and then it is entirely up to you when you respawn (Maximum in 8-9 seconds), whether you respawn at 3 seconds, right immediately or you wait it out, this is entirely up to you.

Next, the game is obviously played actively by a small community, which as far as I'm aware is quite easy-peasy, either no one talks or people greet each other, with others GLHF / GG, which is quite a change seeing it from my side.

Next up, level system, obviously you'd think that a guy with 250 levels is FAR beyond you as 1st time player, wrong you are, everyone has the same chance of killing on another, and even if they stomp you, they ain't making a big deal out of it alike in other games... "Trashplayer", "You suck" or my favorite in my other games "Noob", seems alike this community seems to be quite a nice one.

I give this game a thumbs up, the game mechanics are so simple, yet, very amazingly done by the right people, and I also do appreciate the major fact, that "high level" players ain't toxic to the new ones that in most of the other games seem to be a thing.

Toxic TF2 Main - Out

author: {'steamid': '76561198008587191', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 6, 'playtime_forever': 17382, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 8999, 'last_played': 1699762817}
review:
This is basically an upgrade of Combat Arms. In fact, if memory serves, I believe it was originally going to be called "Combat Arms: Line Of Sight", making it a sequel.

Where Combat Arms was a lot of fun, this game does improve on many aspects, especially the customization of weapons. It also boasts the Unreal Engine, which looks great for a free-to-play game. And then they added more game modes, like a multi-player team death match where players can go co-op against bots. In Combat Arms: Reloaded, you can play against bots.... but only as a single player.

We also have "ESP" matches and "Psionics" matches, the former that lets you use abilities like short-range teleportation or creating medkits from (slowly) regenerating psionic energy (basically like mana or magic points). The latter of the modes includes offensive abilities, like flinging fireballs or dropping entire satellites on your enemy's head.

When I first started playing Line Of Sight, there were 5 different servers to play on. Sadly, since then, 3 of the servers have been removed due to low player count. In fact, there is no longer any U.S. server, so anytime I want to play, I have to pick either Europe or Asia to play on. If we can draw a lot more players, maybe they'll bring back some of the removed servers to give us better ping rates.

In addition, one thing that I don't like in going from Combat Arms: Reloaded to Line Of Sight is that there is no in-game option to record your matches to an .avi or .mp4 file for later viewing. You have to use some form of third party app for that.

I do enjoy the game, it's just hard to find large groups of players to join. As far as gameplay, for a free-to-play game, I would give it a solid 8 out of 10, despite its flaws.

review: Es un muy buen juego hasta ahora lo que he jugado me ha encantado, me gusta todo desde las armas y las habilidades que le podemos poner a nuestros personajes, y un nivel muy bueno de personalizacion del arma, creo que deberian de mejorar un poco el lanzagranadas su radio de daño es bastante pequeño entiendo que puede ser muy op si matara a muchos de un solo tiro pero por lo menos dejarlos heridos no estaria mal y solo matar a alguien directamente si le pega la explosion directo asi que por ese lado ponerle un lanzagranadas a un arma se siente bastante inutil tal vez tambien podrian agregarle una escopeta montable a los rifles de asalto eso estaria bien, el gamplay como los mapas y modos de juegos tambien son muy variados, sin duda recomiendo este juego un muy buen shooter ojala y mas gente lo jugara eso es lo que le hace falta al juego mas promocion aca en latinoamerica y norteamerica.

author: {'steamid': '76561198037297607', 'num_games_owned': 4368, 'num_reviews': 6, 'playtime_forever': 3628, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 3311, 'last_played': 1710119332}
review:
With the shutting down of the USA Servers to this game I might as well leave my final thoughts for this game.  I started playing this a few years ago when it first released and my opinion on it was that, while nothing about it was inherently P2W , the way progressed and how fast you did was effected by it. Waiting for the regular currency in the game to pile up to help pay for attachments or new weapons, was very slow in comparison to dishing out a few bucks for the game's premium currency. 
Aside from that, the voice acting is horrible but the presentation is actually pretty good. The graphics and blood effects are really cool. The game ran pretty smooth for the most part. 
So why does this not get a recommend? Well, aside from the fact the game has been abandoned by both players and developers, the game is also populated by a bunch of whiny LVL 100+ who cry about hacks if they get killed once. I cant possibly imagine why this game was left behind when the only people hosting lobbies are the same whiny losers who block and accuse hacks on anyone coming into this game. I guess you can still play this game if you're EU or someplace else, but anywhere else that isn't covered by the servers, there's really no point to playing this anymore.

author: {'steamid': '76561198172052719', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 14, 'playtime_forever': 24, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 24, 'last_played': 1572986993}
review:
As an FPS Veteran - i can only say that the game has great potential.
It has a lot of weapons to chose from => advanced customization on weapons and char.

It has an anti-cheat system.

And the maps are nice and many

The reloading mechanic was unique - pressing R at the right time for faster reload - rarely seen in an FPS

But what i didn`t liked was :

The maps are too small, from the first game i was already camped by the enemy team and the only instance i left the spawn was after i died 4 times.

The community was a lil bit toxic at the first glance - but i will not judge.

The weapons and modifications are kinda overpriced.

From the first game i got placed in a match with experienced players, with weapons, game skills and time better than mine.

I was frequently naded by the enemies.

Rate - 5/10
Not Really

review: Всем привет,сыграл один раз в эту игру и больше не буду в неё играть .Объясню почему :во время матча первого ,меня убивали ,простите за мат ,нех*й делать .Я не понимаю вообще как  они это делают парой пуль .выходят сразу и дают в жбан (голову ) .Стрельба в этой игре ужасная и недоработанная .Один  человек  наб 50 мать его убийств ,нормально ли играть против того ,кто намного сильнее тебя ?!Дисбаланс в этой игре просто на высшем уровне .Почему то в этой игре авп не убивает с первого раза ...Ужасная игра ,не рекомендую её вам .А ещё здесь нету русского языка,что конечно же является неудобно играть  там .где нету моего родного языка!

author: {'steamid': '76561198264270407', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 1, 'playtime_forever': 251646, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 192013, 'last_played': 1643640110}
review:
Although the game holds something different that shows great promise the developers and GM's of the game do not listen enough to the player base about the bugs and problems of the game aside from the fact that there is never a GM around anymore. 
The player base has shrunk so much that there is not enough to support the game so now its in a vicious cycle of not enough money to support the game which means development is so slow. The only reason I play this game now is because of the group I play with but as soon as we find something else that will be a big chunk of people gone and this is what so many others have done.
Nice community its just unfortunate that the development of Line Of Sight is lacking so much.

review:
Bom, esse e um caso complicado, tenho +500 horas nesse game e digo:

RECOMENDO: 
-FPS bom e divertido
-F2P mas não P2W (as armas pagas são só skin ou são bem ruins)
-Roda em pc meio batata (só bota tudo no low e gg)

NÃO RECOMENDO:	
-Péssima administração 
-Bugs que não foram consertados por pura falta de iniciativa dos devs
- Rest In Peace servidor Br (agr e LAG pra vida)
-Jogo está quase morto

Bug nas conquistas, já completei varias e não caiu na minha Steam (nem ingame), é como se eu não tivesse feito nada, já pedi pros devs resolverem e nada

author: {'steamid': '76561198048893391', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 124, 'playtime_forever': 472, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 323, 'last_played': 1616395345}
review:
Game play is solid,  player base is small, match rewards (have been fixed)

Currency is awarded based on time in the match as well as performance with the time in match being the heavy factor for income.  The game rewards players with enough currency to buy any single gun permanently just by playing a match. Gun costs have come down to a reasonable 17,000 game points.  The game also gives out premium currency for consecutive days played.  

Overall, the game is fun and the developers seem to be listening to critical feedback since changes were made just 2 months after this initial review.


(OPINION - not sure if map is still in game)
The game also has a map called Ground Zero which looks like it takes place in the destroyed area of one of the twin towers which were destroyed in 2001.  I think this is disrespectful to the lives of the 2000 people who died at that location.  And it is for this reason that I will not be playing the game any more.  

Developers, remove Ground Zero from the map selection.  Thank you.

review: from 100 mins of gameplay, a few things are to note: this game dev really likes csgo, and making guns so similar in damage, that there is no reason to pick any. as a level one, i used an m4 and topfragged an s&d with 12 kills, 4 deaths. my team was gross, and only 2 showed potential.  this game probably was made to gain popularity and then transform into a pay to win. the dev himself isn't much of an fps fanboy, this can be picked up from the fact that every fucking gun apparently has 29 rounds and one in the chamber. which can't even be shot because oh wait. this game doesn't understand chambering. the basis of how all magazine guns work. i don't even want to shoot the chambered bullet i just want to be able to have realism in my game. but for me, once you understand that guns should have 31 rounds, one in the chamber and 30 in the clip,  any game who dare assumes that 30 bullets is all you can have at once, is irrelevant. this game is a mashup of everything i hate about a videogame wrapped in one FTP title. it's skins have value, it's guns have no bullet type, (aside from weather or not to pick ap rounds) i mean cmon it's been a year. you game is hot shit. @dev you are wasting money because of ignorance. play shooters like arma before becoming even confident in choosing what type of game you create

author: {'steamid': '76561198237614616', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 45, 'playtime_forever': 69, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 69, 'last_played': 1558953598}
review:
เป็นเกมยิงปืนที่สนุกอีกเกมนึงเลย แต่ถ้าใครเป็น "Motion Sickness FPS" ขั้นรุนแรง "ไม่แนะนำเกมนี้" เพราะมีเกมเพลที่รวดเร็วกว่าเกมยิงปืนหรือเกมFPSชนิดอื่นๆเลยก็ว่าได้ แต่สำหรับใครที่ไม่ได้เป็นโรคดังกล่าว บอกเลยว่าเกมนี้มันมาก ตอบโจทย์ คนที่ชอบ FPS แบบรวดเร็ว และในเวลาเดียวกันก็ต้องใช้เทคนิคการซ่อนตัวและยิงไปอีกด้วยเนื่องจากมีบาง MAP ที่เอื้ออำนวยต่อการแอบซ่อตัวด้วยเช่นกัน
ภาพกราฟฟิกดีสวย สมเป็น Unreal Engine 4
ข้อดีหลักๆ
-แต่งปืนได้ 
-ซื้อปืนได้
-ซื้อตัวละครใหม่ได้ เพราะแต่ละตัวมีความถนัดแตกต่างกันไป รวมถึงสกิลพิเศษที่ออกจะเหนือมนุษย์หน่อยๆ [ย้ำว่าเป็นสกิลนะ ไม่ใช่ Hack]
-อย่างที่บอกตัวละครมีสกิลด้วยแต่ส่วนใหญ่เน้นการใช้อาวุธเป็นหลักเพราะสกิลกว่าจะใช้ได้ก็นานในระดับนึง
-กราฟฟิกสวย [แต่กินสเปคนิดนึง ปรับกาพกลางๆ FPS ผมรีดได้สุด 160 เศษๆ แต่พอ ปรับสุด ได้ 100 ถึง 120 หน่อยๆ ทั้งนี้ทั้งนั้นขึ้นอยู่กับเครื่องPCของพวกคุณแต่ละคนด้วย อันนี้อ้างอิงจากเครื่องของผมเอง]
-ปิงไม่เยอะเท่าไรนะ [ถ้าเล่นเซิฟ SEA]
-เกมมีหลายโหมดหลายด่านให้เลือก

ข้อเสียหลักๆ
-เกมนี้เนื่องจากออกมานานพอสมควร ผู้เล่นในแต่ละเซิฟอาจจะน้อยไปก็จริง โดยเฉพาะ SEA แต่อย่างไรก็ตาม หากเป็นช่วงปิดเทอม ก็จะมีคนเพิ่มเข้ามาอีกพอสมควร วันหยุด ก็ยังพอหาคนได้ 

สรุป : 70/100 คะแนน -30 อันเนื่องมากจาก ไม่สามารถแก้ปัญหาหรือการเชิญชวนดึงดูดให้ผู้เล่นมาเล่นกันเยอะๆได้ [คนน้อยอะว่าง่ายๆ]
แต่ถ้ามีเพื่อนๆจำนวนมากที่เล่น เกมFPSละก็ มีเกมนี้เก็บไว้ก็ไม่เสียหาย เพราะเกมนี้ "โหลดฟรี ไฟล์ตอนติดตั้ง 2.4 GB"

author: {'steamid': '76561198373502045', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 197, 'playtime_forever': 1664, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 1610, 'last_played': 1675456109}
review:
I really want to recommend this game but I just can’t at the moment. I enjoy playing it and it brings back so many good memories of MW2 but there are just too many problems with it currently. If the devs fix/change anything I'll update my review.
Pros
Weapon/Character Customization
Not Pay to Win (Yes I'm serious)
Runs good
High TTK
Classic Vibe
Weapon Balance (Pretty good, there are a few weps that need a nerf atm though.)

Cons
Hitreg - Terrible atm, constantly die around corners
Hit boxes - Same with hitreg
Head glitching - Major problem that needs fixing
GP earn rate - Needs to be increased or weapon prices lowered
Mantle/Flash Animation - Are terrible and get you killed so much and need to be removed.
Player falling physics - don't try to slide down a hill
Flashlight - I get its a tactical light but it shouldn't be like looking at the sun
Maps - Pretty meh, a lot of them could use adjusting.
"Super Powers/Abilities" - I hate them, but I play classic anyways
UI - Could be simpler

If you want to read it properly formatted: http://steamcommunity.com/id/Juggernaut_Drive/recommended/436520/

I'll try to expand on my points in case anyone is interested in more of what I mean. Before that however I do want to mention that I do enjoy the game. I enjoy it so much and it reminds me of when I used to play COD all day on xbox when I was a kid. Now to get to the points.

The Pros:
Weapon/Character Customization - Nothing much to say just it's pretty in depth and you can make so many different variants. The only real thing their lacking here are the skins. I assume they will add more skins in time though.
Not Pay to Win - It's not pay to win which is great! People who say it's pay to win don't put any time into the game and look don't at the weapon stats. If you did than you would find out that most of the weapons you buy don't have any better stats that the ones you start with. Now of course there are some weapons that are better than others atm but you get that with every AAA game that has a price tag of ~$60 so I'm sure the developers will address those in the future.
Runs good - Nothing more to say really. It runs good and I have had no problems with it.
High TTK - Very high time to kill which is great. But if you pair that with bad hitreg then you get a load of problems (hitreg is talked about more below).
Classic Vibe - Reminds me of the COD4/MW2 days.
Weapon Balance - As talked about in the not p2w section, weapon balance is pretty good at the time of this review.

The Cons:
Hitreg - It's really bad atm and I mean REALLY bad. Your shots don't hit and you die around corners constantly. I don't know if I just didn't notice it when I first started playing, but I noticed it after one of their updates. So I'm not sure if it was always bad or if that update broke it.
Hit boxes - The female hitbox is smaller than the males (not the bad point) but when you have bad hitreg/head glitching it makes you thing that the hit boxes are also broken. I don't know if it’s that or the hitreg, but something is definitely off.
Head glitching - Major problem that needs fixing. You see the tippy top of their head and they see your whole body. Plus, pair that with the hitboxes and you can't hit their head.
GP earn rate - Needs to be increased or weapon prices lowered. I have around 28 hours into the game (not all playtime) and I currently have around ~170,000 GP. Which seems like a lot of GP but when you add that I played very heavily during the valentine event and the new achievements I got (since it was a new account) it's really not that much. If it wasn't a valentine event and I wasn't a new player I would have significantly less GP for that time played. Yes yes I know you get GP from missions, achievements, leaderboard rankings and at the end of every match.
Missions - Math is based off a 30 day month. So if you do EVERY single mission a month you get around 114,000GP. Daily Missions = 90,000GP, Weekly Missions = 12,000GP, Monthly Missions = 12,000GP. So 1 month of my time isn't worth enough for ONE primary weapon (about 214,000GP)?
Achievements - Yes you get GP for achievements and you get the reward ONCE. This seems good and fair since there are 408 achievements but it's not. More than like half of the achievements are weapon related which means you CAN'T get the reward until you unlock the weapon. The weapons go as follows; K2 I = 30 kills, K2 II = 300 kills, K2 III = 3000 kills. I shouldn't have to say much more about why relying on achievements for GP is so stupid.
Leaderboard - You get 20,000GP if you place in the top 4% in every section every month.
End of match reward - You get like 100GP which is pointless. 1000 games of 100GP = 100,000GP.
Mantle/Flash Animation - Are terrible and get you killed so much and need to be removed. There stupid animations that are not needed. The flash puts a hand up in front of your view and you can’t shoot until the hand goes down. It also lasts LONGER than the actual flash like wtf. The mantle locks you into a mantle animation when you try and jump over something.
Player falling physics - You get stuck and jitter down the hill or object that’s slanted.
Flash light - I get its a tactical light but it shouldn't be like looking at the sun. It's gameplay breaking, way to bright atm.
Maps - Pretty meh, a lot of them could use adjusting. The S&D maps are by far the best but come with problems as well. A lot of the sites only have 2 entrances and then its closed off.
"Super Powers/Abilities" - Hate them since you need to have the medic one equipped or you’re at a huge disadvantage.
UI - Very confusing when you first load it up and could be simpler.

review:
本游戏极其不推荐国人入坑 
1.武器改造需要大量的GP但是收入非常少
2.武器购买永久除了副武器基本都是10w+而一把的收益大概在150到300之间
3.虽然没特别大的氪金压制 但是还是有的只是不算大而已
4.画面很差  绝对不是你在steam看到的截图那样 特效全开地面效果堪比cf （个人配置1060）
5.现在基本没啥人打了

review:
Overall, i love this game already. There are only 2 things that could be possibly improved:
Battle Royale Mode - I mean, it can only start with 9+ players and that results in a huuuge waiting time.
Overall textures - shaders are just perfect, but i'd love if there was an option for HD textures or something. Even on highest settings the textures still aren't really that good.

But hey, it's the gaming experience itself that counts most!
And this game?
Oh boy, you're in for one hell of a ride!

author: {'steamid': '76561198869856761', 'num_games_owned': 19, 'num_reviews': 24, 'playtime_forever': 1629, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 1449, 'last_played': 1622455557}
review:
24시간한 초보입니다. 이게임은 고인물이 많고 아이템빨이 엄청납니다. 안하는걸 추천드립니다.  실력만 있으면 템빨을 억제할수 있긴 한데 최소 10시간은 해야 실력이 생깁니다. 다른 fps하시길 바랍니다. 추천 진짜 안드립니다. 저는 재미있게 했지만 방이 더럽게 없습니다. 파츠빨도 상당하고 총빨도 상당해 실력은 큰 비중을 차지하지 못합니다. 그리고 초능력같은게 있다보니 게임성은 신박하다고 봅니다. 서버상태가 개판이지만요. 그레서 요즘엔 배그나 글옵 링엘들을 하고있지요 2주동안은 한번도 안한것 같네요

평가
그래픽-높음
서버 상태- 매우 최악
총 종류- 복합적
진입장벽-높음
사양- 낮음
최종점수- 복합적

author: {'steamid': '76561198071783906', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 101, 'playtime_forever': 174, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 174, 'last_played': 1554155585}
review:
"RÁLÁTÁS"

A 'Line of Sight ' tulajdonképpen egy fura MOBA/FPS egyvelege,van itten fizetős (PaytoWin) részleg,és farmolgatós ingyenesdi is.

"Tápos Terminátor 2.O."

Karakterkészítés,és már ugorhatunk is fejest ebbe a nem mindennapi shooterba.Egy gyors 'Training',és azt is megtanuljuk hogyan kell az ellen-re hívni egy  halom ócskavasat (mosógép,űrhajórocs,csövek) egyvelegét tűzgolyó formájában ami bizonyos területre hat.Továbbá karakterünk képes egy ún. 'Dash' képességre-ez olyan mint valami Jedi erő amivel "ide-oda" tologathatjuk magunkat...közben karakterünk egyik keze kék (állandóan) árnyalatokban villog,mint valami rendőrautó.

Indinánok kontra Cowboyok

Igen van a játékban egy dobófejszeszerűség,amitől egy-kettőre Apacsokká transformálódhatunk,és újraírhatjuk a nagy  Indián versus  spanyolok (főbb)csatáit,csak modern köntösben.A dobófejszével hatalmasakat suhinthatunk,sőt akár hozzá is vághatjuk az ellenfelünkhöz,majd mihelyst ez megtörtént amaz hanyatt-homlok csuklik össze.

Egy szó mint száz,kellemes időtöltést eredményez eme,csoda,s rövid ideig talán bepillantást nyerhetünk a régi nagy Apacs háborúkba. Élien voltam

review:
To be honest, the game is complete garbage.
-Almost dead, there are like 4 servers
-The visuals are terrible, tearing and other visual bugs
-The community is 2/3 times non-English speakers
-The hitboxes are complete garbage
-Hackers rampid
-Devs have completely abandoned the game
-Extremely hard to get the money to customize the weapons in the game as well as characters
-All of the guns are the same; one to two shot kills
-Almost non existent recoil for ALL guns
In conclusion:
Its a waste of hard drive space and shouldn't be touched. Just don't even try. Its terrible.

author: {'steamid': '76561198353536384', 'num_games_owned': 146, 'num_reviews': 9, 'playtime_forever': 45, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 45, 'last_played': 1494701725}
review: This game had such good potential, however, the execution was terrible. I saw the game play, and I was impressed. Upon playing it, however, I was very disappointed. The weapons were terrible. They were unbalanced, and very awkward to use. The game mechanics were unbalanced and useless. Using special abilities would sometimes drain the player of his health. The actual game play was not like the trailer at all. The trailer shows very competitive action, while actual game play consists of players spawning all across the map, running to find a fight, dying, then waiting for respawn. It was very boring, as well as grueling, and I had a better time watching paint dry than attempting to play this game. If you want to get a free FPS, I would suggest Counter Strike: Global Offensive, Warface, Black Squad, or Dirty Bomb. Do not waste time on this game.

review:
Don't waste your time on playing this game. For a long time devs only add new items to buy for real money instead of fixing annoying bugs or adding new content etc.
Generally the game is managed badly, e.g.: Recently they organized an event that players could win real money by playing. It seemed nice at first. But it was SCAM in some way. They announced winners only in Steam Announcements (not in game, nor Facebook etc.), in an unexpected random day, quite a long time after event, and they set the deadline to claim the awards only to next day, so there was to little time to even notice this announcement.

author: {'steamid': '76561198441473579', 'num_games_owned': 71, 'num_reviews': 5, 'playtime_forever': 97, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 97, 'last_played': 1549887381}
review:
这个游戏玩了一会。。还是有点想法的
首先这个游戏有点COD的感觉，射击手感还好
还有枪械改装功能，东西蛮多的还可以魔改，这点我很喜欢
游戏提供射击场可以测试枪穿透能力便携程度还有距离等等
游戏提供的模式还是比较多但是没啥人
BUT
这个游戏对待新手不平衡，人太少
辅助能力（瞬移除外）几乎没什么模式能用，自己创房间也不知道为什么有密码设置栏但设不了（百度没有解答）
当然免费游戏毕竟很少像Dirty bomb这种完全不用氪金的，也就是说这个LINE OF SIGHT 是一个氪金游戏
这里最贵的货币是钻石，短时间需要大量的钻石靠氪金，一部分好武器也要靠钻石
不过刚开始把你的M4改一改也可以玩过去
当然你也可以不买抢改枪，上战场捡别人的枪用就行了
有些人太nb了打不过是常态，习惯就好
最后
我觉得这个游戏还行，起码过得去
希望对你有用

review:
Я держал руку в овраге,
Вандерлей пришел и пришел, чтобы дать неверную идею
Он повернулся ко мне и сделал предложение:
Оплетка с кучей скатов

Это моя жизнь, я чувствую запах пыли и горю камень,
Взбираюсь на пикник, а потом курю травку.
Используя высокие наркотики и любя собаку,
Проповедовать сатанизм и практиковать фелляцию

Песо Брасука 1 мая в 1:55
Я держал его рукой в ​​сломанной па пум
и я получаю один, и я говорю
Ты хочешь умереть до смерти?
следовательно, сломанный впал в смех
ниггер тупее моей бабушки с амнезией с лихорадкой Эбола и AVC
YA derzhal ruku v ovrage,
Vanderley prishel i prishel, chtoby dat' nevernuyu ideyu
On povernulsya ko mne i sdelal predlozheniye:
Opletka s kuchey skatov

Eto moya zhizn', ya chuvstvuyu zapakh pyli i goryu kamen',
Vzbirayus' na piknik, a potom kuryu travku.
Ispol'zuya vysokiye narkotiki i lyubya sobaku,
Propovedovat' satanizm i praktikovat' fellyatsiyu

Peso Brasuka 1 maya v 1:55
YA derzhal yego rukoy v ​​slomannoy pa pum
i ya poluchayu odin, i ya govoryu
Ty khochesh' umeret' do smerti?

author: {'steamid': '76561198321782248', 'num_games_owned': 89, 'num_reviews': 7, 'playtime_forever': 231, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 231, 'last_played': 1549504380}
review:
1	Em uma panela de fundo largo, derreta o açúcar até ficar dourado.
2	Junte meia xícara (chá) de água quente e mexa com uma colher.
3	Deixe ferver até dissolver os torrões de açúcar e a calda engrossar.
4	Forre com a calda uma forma com furo central (19 cm de diâmetro) e reserve.
Pudim:
5	Em um liquidificador, bata todos os ingredientes do pudim e despeje na forma reservada.
6	Cubra com papel-alumínio e leve ao forno médio (180°C), em banho-maria, por cerca de 1 hora e 30 minutos.
7	Depois de frio, leve para gelar por cerca de 6 horas. Desenforme e sirva a seguir.
DICAS:
- É essencial que o pudim seja preparado em banho-maria para que asse de forma lenta e controlada, para atingir a textura ideal. 
- Para que o seu pudim não forme furinhos, verifique se a temperatura do forno está regulada conforme indicação da receita. Leve a forma ao forno na grade superior, longe da chama.

review:
LINE OF SIGHT, o que dizer deste jogo? 

Bom, ele foi um dos primeiros jogos que eu joguei quando criei minha conta na Steam. Tudo travando, e mesmo assim eu ainda era bom, tinha muitas salas pra jogar e talz. Mas...infelizmente tudo foi por água abaixo quando eu reinstalei o jogo hoje...e vi que não tem mais nenhuma sala cheia.
   Só tinha UMA SALA na América do sul, e apenas quatro jogadores(eu e mais três). O que eu mais gostei nesse jogo foi o fato de ter me ajudado a melhorar em jogos de tiro multiplayer, pq no início, mano, eu era um asno jogando. E depois d eum tempo, eu melhorei bastante, e hoje eu jogo vários jogos assim. Mas infelizmente tudo desapareceu em um piscar de olhos, o jogo simplesmente...morreu pra mim.

Com total sinceridade, eu não sei se eu recomendo ou não, mas já que eu sou obrigado a decidir um...

review:
отыграл в ней 2 часа и понял,что игра полная дич,обычный такой шутерок с МИЛЛИАРДОМ ДОНАТА КОТОРЫЙ РЕШАЕТ ВСЁ.К примеру,я новичок зашол пограть и игру,тебя кидает к таким же новичкам как и ты,многие  скажут "йоу а что тут такого?".НО!Эти навички все с донат пушками и в броне,и без гранаты или суперспособноси его нормально не завалиш.про читер вообще молчу,на каждм сервере аимшик который стоит всю катку на мнесте и убивает всех аимом.Вобщем не рекомнедую,игра полнейший калл как Point Blank или ROS.
Ставлю 2 читера из 10 + 1 балл за креативность с суперспособностями.

author: {'steamid': '76561198193223709', 'num_games_owned': 332, 'num_reviews': 72, 'playtime_forever': 896, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 573, 'last_played': 1657898925}
review:
Pay To Win under disguise!

At the start of the game, you can't buy any guns except for a few, which are lackluster!
You are given a few guns for 30 days which will then expire, and then you'll be stuck with the Training M4 which cannot be tuned. That means you can't attach a scope or anything like that, which will then get you killed as the long range targets will be very hard to shoot. There's a lot of long range shooting, camping, and sniping in this game. Also as a new player you will be put against the high level players who have unlocked the better guns. Earning enough gold to buy a gun after it becomes unlockable for gold when you level up will take forever as well! That's right, if you want to get good gear to be able compete better at the start when you're going up against the pros who will beat you anyway; expect to pay real cash! This game is absolutely trash and the developers are unashamed to lie about it! Oh and by the way, you can't rent weapons to try them out and there's no selling back attachments or guns if you accidentally buy the wrong item. Matchmaking well is trash, like I mentioned before you'll get put against pro but also the game is almost dead.

The only good thing is the customization. If you want a scope on a Glock 18, you can put one on it although that would be perfectly useless as it can't shoot that far.

The graphics are just ok, there's plenty of vegetation but it's all low res compared to newer titles. At least the game is very passable graphically due to it's small download size.

Overall -666/5 stars!



Do yourself a favor and play other FREE games instead, emphasis on FREE!

Completely free games, no microtransactions, no DLC, no purchases of any sort!

La location d'armes ne me dérange pas mais comment je gagne de la thune in game et de l'xp si le lancement plante en permanence, je ne sais pas si je dois le recommander ou le désinstaller définitivement à cause de bugs idiots!

author: {'steamid': '76561198057894301', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 54, 'playtime_forever': 29, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 29, 'last_played': 1544354427}
review: Play another and better online FPS. I just felt like trying this cause back then when I felt like trying Crossfire, Counter Strike, A.V.A I had a good time. The controls are just so clunky and feels so stiff, you can't switch to knife instantly after firing a sniper shot. And the maps are way too small. Go ahead and play a FFA mode, chances are you will be randomyl spawned behind an enemy you're not even aware of and get killed after just taking a few steps. The team deathmatches are ok but the maps are just way too small. There is no room for strategy, just spray your bullets, throw grenades and hopefully somebody will get killed. This game still needs some work, some fine tuning.

review:
จากประสบการณที่เล่นเกมห่านนี้มานาน เมื่อหลายปีก่อนนั้นเกมห่านี้ค่อนข้างไปได้สวยที่เดียว ได้เจอคนไทยดีๆ หลายๆคนก็เกมนี้เลยแหละสำหรับผมนะ แต่ถ้ามาระยะหลังไม่มีการอัพเดตหรือแก้ไขอะไรเลยด่านบางด่านก็ลอกเกมอื่นมาสิ่งที่มีเอกลักษณ์ของเกมนี้ มันมีแหละแต่ไม่ไม่เคยปรับปรุง ให้มันดีขึ้นเลยสึกนิดเลย ESP บางอย่างบัคตั้งแต่ 2-3 ปีก่อนตอนนี้ก็ยังไม่แก้ และระยะหลังจากที่ เซิพ ASIA บินไปก็ต้องไปเล่นกะอีพวก EU อีฝั่ง EU ก็ไล่มาเซิพ ASIA 

สำหรับผมแล้ว ผมชอบเกมนี้นะแต่ คุณอยากจะเติบโตกับเกมที่ DEV ไม่พัฒนาสิ่งใหม่ๆเข้ามาในเกมไหมละ


หากเห็นผมเล่นเกมนี้ต่อไป ก็เหมือนแบบมาแวะบ้านเพื่อนที่ไม่ได้เจอกันนานดีกว่า
ไม่ห้ามคนที่อยากเล่นนะครับ แต่เกมแม่งมาได้แค่นี้แหละ


ปล.อย่าตัดต่อรูปว่าตัวเอง hack นะเออ มีคนโดนแบนเพราะ แกล้งบอกว่าตัวเอง hack มาละ

คนน้อย เกมไม่มีการพัฒนาต่อ เหมือนตันอยู่แค่นี้ อย่าเล่นเลยครับ

review:
與其說是CF。。。我覺得更像是SF2（或者國服應該叫做風暴戰區？連氪金方向都挺像）[spoiler]還沒SF2的人物好看[/spoiler]

[list]
[*]有中文哦

[*]免費的呦

[*]槍械可以自定義（只是外觀和配件的裝卸，需要花費遊戲幣購買配件，塗裝則是消耗代幣），不過並沒能允許玩家改的很誇張，數值方面也只是有略微的影響，追求某一屬性提升並不會有[u][b]很大代價[/b][/u]

↑因為武器後坐力沒那麼明顯接近cod的感覺[spoiler]激光槍[/spoiler]

[*]新手送一個月的各式槍械以及一位女性角色還有大量遊戲幣，其數量完全足夠玩家購買一兩把主武器甚至完全改裝。

[*]除了常規fps該有的，奔跑跳躍肩瞄以外，還有技能系統，可以自己搭配兩個主動技能（進攻技能和輔助或增強技能），算是蠻有趣的啦。[spoiler]雖然有腳架這個東西，但是，不能趴下[/spoiler]

[*]不能滑行

[*]男女角色有數值上的差距

[*]靶場的設計很棒，而且可以在改裝武器的時候進入靶場測試目前的搭配（好像M200是唯一一把可以擊穿地面材質打到靶子的武器？？）

[*]UI設計咱挺喜歡的

[*]每日簽到就給代幣，一個月滿簽大概能有250左右代幣，一個消費代幣購買的角色需要1200代幣，這麼看來。。。還是蠻良心的喔？

[*]第一人稱蠻棒的，左右180度範圍內移動視角角色是只運動上半身的，可以低頭看看自己的腳，是不會動的，而且每個主動技能的使用也會有不同的第一人稱/第三人稱動作變化。[spoiler]其實就是想說人物動作比較豐富hhh[/spoiler]

[*]人很少，各個服務器的玩家都不怎麼多

[*]團隊競賽AI模式很有趣，出現的AI竟然全都使用的玩家的信息和裝備，是前一天排行榜前數位的玩家

[*]看看商店頁的視頻也知道，其實遊戲還是蠻酷的。

[*]實際遊戲畫面並沒有商店頁面來的那麼好，特別是人物的模型，我都不敢相信這是韓國做的遊戲。。。

[*]分辨率不支持超寬屏（咱用的是29寸屏幕）

[/list]

總之作為免費遊戲其實還好啦，甚至還送玩家代幣，只簽到就能攢好多代幣隨便花了。

咱還是想玩一玩那個CO-OP模式。。。然而完全沒有人玩這個模式，一個人又不能開始，氣死。

review:
Veamos, es como si Battlefield 4 tuviese un hijo, y ese niño (no estoy asumiendo su genero) tuviese poderes. Podrá ser gratis y bastante facil de jugar, pero tiene sus defectos: Falta de jugadores, mala optimización de renders a distancia, las miras con magnificación parecen sacadas de un juego de guerra viejo, las armas no son "costosas" pero para conseguir el dinero o usas dinero real o juegas partidas, suerte encontrando con quien jugar.
Solo porque realmente se parece a BF4 (en dimensiones pequeñas) le doy un 8.5/10

author: {'steamid': '76561198855431349', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 8, 'playtime_forever': 2396, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 900, 'last_played': 1545356739}
review: Устав от PUBG, Black Squad ,CSGO, Варфейса (не люблю наши проекты),Героев и генералов (играл во все это на другом акке). Наткнулся на эту игрушку и был приятно удивлен. На ультрах выдает в районе 80-100 фпс а картинка довольно таки приятная! Пластиковая физика напоминает кс го, но она как раз кстати для любителей авм. Странно, что ранее не заметил эту игру.Есть даже батлл рояль.  На картах с закладкой бомбы - весело. Короче попробовать стоит.Донат вообще не нужен все пушки со временем даже за донат , доступны за игровую валюту,стоит лишь подождать пока они откроются. Минусы= единственное, я не понял сперва почему такое разрешение оружия в игре изначально, выкрутил на максимум и все стало довольно таки приятным.
